### List runtime bindings
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dataplane/bindings

### Check dataplane consumer readiness
GET http://127.0.0.1:8088/readyz

### Check validator readiness
GET http://127.0.0.1:8089/readyz

### Upsert runtime binding
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dataplane/bindings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "orders",
  "kafka_topic": "mr.orders"
}

### Upsert validation config
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dataplane/configs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "orders-required",
  "binding": "orders",
  "version": "v1",
  "rules": [
    {"field": "account_id", "kind": "required"},
    {"field": "account_id", "kind": "not_empty"},
    {"field": "status", "kind": "equals", "expected": "OPEN"}
  ]
}

### Activate validation config
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dataplane/configs/activate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "binding": "orders",
  "version": "v1"
}

### List active configs
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dataplane/configs?active=true

### Emit valid scenario through server edge
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dataplane/emulator/emit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "binding": "orders",
  "scenario": "valid"
}

### Emit invalid scenario through server edge
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dataplane/emulator/emit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "binding": "orders",
  "scenario": "missing_required"
}

### List latest validation results
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dataplane/results?binding=orders&limit=10

### Query one validation result by message_id
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dataplane/results?message_id=replace-with-message-id

### Query latest result by correlation_id
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/dataplane/results?correlation_id=replace-with-correlation-id&limit=1
